# Dlib 68-point Facial Landmark Model
# 
# IMPORTANT: This is a placeholder file. You need to download the actual model file.
#
# Download the model from:
# http://dlib.net/files/shape_predictor_68_face_landmarks.dat.bz2
#
# After downloading:
# 1. Extract the .bz2 file to get shape_predictor_68_face_landmarks.dat
# 2. Place it in the project root directory (same location as this file)
# 3. Remove this placeholder file
#
# The model file is approximately 95MB when extracted.
# This is required for the facial landmark detection functionality.
#
# Alternative download sources:
# - https://github.com/italojs/facial-landmarks-recognition/blob/master/shape_predictor_68_face_landmarks.dat
# - https://github.com/PyImageSearch/imutils/blob/master/examples/shape_predictor_68_face_landmarks.dat
